---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Financial Calculators - WestGroup Financial Planning | Free Retirement & Investment Tools"
  description="Professional financial planning calculators for retirement planning, investment growth, tax optimization, and net worth analysis. Free tools for high-net-worth individuals in British Columbia."
  canonical="https://westgroupfinancial.com/calculator/"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-yellow-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-green-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight font-['Playfair_Display']">
          <span class="text-white">Financial</span><br>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400">Calculators</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Professional-grade financial planning tools designed for high-net-worth individuals. 
          Get instant insights into your retirement, investment, and tax planning strategies.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-yellow-400/25 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
            Schedule Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="border border-yellow-400 text-yellow-400 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all duration-300">
            View Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Calculator Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 font-['Playfair_Display']">
          <span class="text-white">Financial</span>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400"> Calculators</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Plan your financial future with our comprehensive suite of calculators designed for high-net-worth individuals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Retirement Calculator -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-yellow-400/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-yellow-400/10 fade-in stagger-1">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
            </svg>
            Retirement Planning Calculator
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Current Age</label>
                <input type="number" value="35" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-yellow-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Retirement Age</label>
                <input type="number" value="65" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-yellow-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Current Savings ($)</label>
                <input type="number" value="100000" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-yellow-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Monthly Contribution ($)</label>
                <input type="number" value="2000" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-yellow-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Expected Annual Return (%)</label>
              <input type="number" value="7" step="0.1" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-yellow-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400/10 to-green-400/10 border border-yellow-400/30 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 font-['Playfair_Display']">Sample Retirement Projection</h4>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
                <div class="bg-gray-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-1">$2,400,000</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Projected Total at 65</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-1">$8,000</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Monthly Income Available</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">30+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Years of Income</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <a href="/contact" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 text-slate-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-yellow-400/25 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
                Get Personalized Analysis
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Investment Growth Calculator -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-green-400/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-green-400/10 fade-in stagger-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
            Investment Growth Calculator
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Initial Investment ($)</label>
                <input type="number" value="50000" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-green-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Investment Period (Years)</label>
                <input type="number" value="10" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-green-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Expected Return (%)</label>
                <input type="number" value="8" step="0.1" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-green-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">Annual Contribution ($)</label>
                <input type="number" value="12000" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-green-400 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-400/20 transition-all duration-300 focus-ring">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400/10 to-yellow-400/10 border border-green-400/30 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">Sample Investment Projection</h4>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Future Value:</span>
                  <span class="text-green-400 font-bold text-xl">$284,000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Total Contributions:</span>
                  <span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">$170,000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Investment Gains:</span>
                  <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">$114,000</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <a href="/contact" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-yellow-400 text-slate-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-green-400/25 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
                Get Professional Advice
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Calculators Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-3">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 font-['Playfair_Display']">Tax Planning Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Calculate potential tax savings through strategic planning and optimization.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-300 font-medium transition-colors duration-200">Schedule Consultation</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-4">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16l3-3m-3 3l-3-3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 font-['Playfair_Display']">Estate Planning Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Estimate estate taxes and plan efficient wealth transfer strategies.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-300 font-medium transition-colors duration-200">Schedule Consultation</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-5">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2-2v2m8 0H8m8 0v2a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002 2V6z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 font-['Playfair_Display']">Business Valuation Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Estimate your business value for succession and exit planning purposes.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-300 font-medium transition-colors duration-200">Schedule Consultation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Indicators Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-800/30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
          Why Trust <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400">WestGroup?</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="fade-in stagger-1">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">25+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Years in Business</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-in stagger-2">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">BBB A+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Rating</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-in stagger-3">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">Licensed</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">& Insured</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-in stagger-4">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">Family</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Owned</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800/80 to-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl p-12 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-['Playfair_Display']">
          Get Professional Analysis
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          While these calculators provide valuable insights, nothing replaces personalized analysis from experienced 
          fee-only fiduciary advisors. Schedule your complimentary consultation today.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-yellow-400/25 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            Schedule Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="border border-yellow-400 text-yellow-400 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
            Explore Our Services
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-6">No obligation • Confidential discussion • Immediate insights</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
